### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@username = dev_user
@password = Password123!

### 1. Registrar Usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 2. Login (Capturar o Token)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

#### Guardar Token
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 3. Acessar Perfil (Protegido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 4. Perfil sem Token (Deve falhar)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
